  "title": "🚑 Ambulance Driver (EMS – EMTD) | Up to $3,000 + Allowances + Bonuses",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚑 Ambulance Driver (EMS – EMTD) | Up to $3,000 + Allowances + Bonuses</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Islandwide</p><p><strong>Work Type:</strong> Full-time | Shift-based</p><p><strong>Salary Range:</strong> Up to $3,000 + Allowances + Bonuses</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>Take the wheel of emergency response as an <strong>Emergency Medical Technician Driver (EMTD)! </strong>You’ll be part of a <strong>team </strong>in ensuring <strong>safe and timely ambulance conveyance</strong>.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive the ambulance safely and efficiently during emergency responses</li><li>Assist Paramedics and EMTs in providing pre-hospital emergency care</li><li>Ensure vehicle readiness and compliance with operational standards</li><li>Conduct routine ambulance checks, equipment maintenance, and documentation</li><li>Uphold professionalism and service excellence in high-stress environments</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>✅ <strong>Emergency Medical Technician (EMT) Course</strong> recognized by the Ministry of Health (MOH)</p><p>✅ <strong>Valid Class 3 Driving Licence</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Career Pathways:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Career progression </strong>opportunities</li><li>Eligible for <strong>education sponsorship</strong></li><li>Eligible for <strong>Class 4 driving training</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><ul><li>Gain <strong>exclusive EMS driving experience</strong> without a long-term bond</li><li>Access <strong>structured training and certifications</strong> not available elsewhere</li><li>Enjoy <strong>stable allowances, bonuses, and shift flexibility</strong></li><li>Opportunity to <strong>advance into leadership or Paramedic roles</strong></li><li>Be part of a <strong>mission-driven team</strong> that saves lives every day</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to Drive with Purpose?</strong></p><p>Join Singapore’s emergency frontliners and take the wheel of meaningful service.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Apply now and kickstart your career in EMS today!</strong></p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to:<strong> Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</strong></p><p>Please include your<strong> availability, notice period, and expected salary.</strong></p><p>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435</p>",
